1. *Ponedeljak* je prvi radni dan u nedelji. (Monday is the first working day of the week.)
2. *Ponedeljkom* počinje novi radni tjedan. (Monday starts a new work week.)
3. Dan koji slijedi *ponedeljak* je utorak. (The day after Monday is Tuesday.)
4. Trgovine su zatvorene *ponedeljkom*. (Stores are closed on Monday.)
5. U *ponedeljak* ćemo obaviti sastanak. (We will have a meeting on Monday.)